verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H5921"\w* end, \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Core.

\w O|strong="H0430"\w* clap \w your|strong="H4672"\w* hands, \w all|strong="H3966"\w* ye nations: shout unto \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w with|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H4672"\w* voice \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Joy,

\w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H0776"\w* high, terrible: \w a|strong="H5921"\w* great \w king|strong="H5921"\w* \w over|strong="H5921"\w* all \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w earth|strong="H0776"\w*.
\w He|strong="H4325"\w* hath subdued \w the|strong="H2022"\w* people under us; \w and|strong="H2022"\w* \w the|strong="H2022"\w* nations under our feet.

\w He|strong="H0430"\w* hath chosen \w for|strong="H0430"\w* \w us|strong="H8055"\w* \w his|strong="H0430"\w* inheritance \w the|strong="H0430"\w* beauty \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Jacob which \w he|strong="H0430"\w* hath loved.

\w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w is|strong="H0430"\w* ascended \w with|strong="H0430"\w* jubilee, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6437"\w* Lord \w with|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6437"\w* sound \w of|strong="H0430"\w* trumpet.
Sing praises \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* \w God|strong="H5414"\w*, sing ye: sing praises \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* king, sing ye.
\w For|strong="H6635"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* king \w of|strong="H0430"\w* all \w the|strong="H3068"\w* earth: sing ye wisely.

\w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* reign \w over|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* \w nations|strong="H0776"\w*: \w God|strong="H3068"\w* sitteth \w on|strong="H0776"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* holy throne.

\w The|strong="H5704"\w* princes \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w people|strong="H0776"\w* \w are|strong="H0776"\w* gathered together, \w with|strong="H8313"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* God \w of|strong="H0776"\w* Abraham: \w for|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* strong gods \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w earth|strong="H0776"\w* \w are|strong="H0776"\w* exceedingly exalted.
